Detailed Description

Simple class for iterating over the children of a SceneNode, serves as a simple iterator.

Remarks:
Using the SceneNode removeChildSceneNode and destroyChildSceneNode methods can invalidate instances of this class if the removed or destroyed SceneNode happens to be the one the SceneNodeIterator currently points to.
